title: Sarah Dunsey, 17, who went missing from Las Vegas hotel was NOT kidnapped, cops say – despite her family insisting she was taken by ‘people traffickers’
text:
Opinion 'KIDNAPPING' MYSTERY DEEPENS Sarah Dunsey, 17, who went missing from Las Vegas hotel was NOT kidnapped, cops say – despite her family insisting she was taken by ‘people traffickers’ 
Police confirmed the teen also appeared to leave 'willingly' when she was seen in the company of two men By Zoe Nauman US Online Reporter 23rd February 2017, 2:16 am
